    <item>
      <title>强硬派向议长约翰逊施压，要求他在支出协议上食言</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/hardliners-pressure-speaker-johnson-to-renege-on-spending-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几位共和党人周四表示，众议院议长迈克·约翰逊正在积极讨论废除与民主党的支出协议，以安抚其不安的右翼，距离资金失效引发部分政府关门仅剩八天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/hardliners-pressure-speaker-johnson-to-renege-on-spending-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 18:15:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚可怕的夏季野火被潮湿的天气浸透</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/australia-s-dreaded-summer-of-wildfires-soaked-by-wet-weather</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚正准备迎接酷暑和野火的回归，但该国东部却面临着长期的暴雨，房屋被淹没，从糖到小麦的农作物受损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/australia-s-dreaded-summer-of-wildfires-soaked-by-wet-weather</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷 161 亿美元判决现已开放领取</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/argentina-s-16-1-billion-from-ypf-now-fair-game-for-collection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[寻求从阿根廷 2012 年收购石油公司 YPF SA 的法院判决中追回 161 亿美元的投资者可以开始追索其资产，因为一名美国法官裁定阿根廷不得推迟这些追收工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/argentina-s-16-1-billion-from-ypf-now-fair-game-for-collection</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 17:43:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>律师告诉法官，特朗普欺诈审判基于政治议程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/trump-fraud-trial-based-on-political-agenda-lawyer-tells-judge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统的律师告诉将对此案做出裁决的法官，纽约州针对唐纳德·特朗普的欺诈指控是由政治对手炮制的，该州为期三个月的民事审判“没有证据”表明他在资产价值方面误导了银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/trump-fraud-trial-based-on-political-agenda-lawyer-tells-judge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 17:29:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦获得国际货币基金组织最终批准 7 亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/pakistan-secures-final-imf-approval-for-700-million-loan-tranche</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦最终获得国际货币基金组织 (IMF) 批准发放约 7 亿美元的援助，为下个月选举前陷入困境的南亚经济提供提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/pakistan-secures-final-imf-approval-for-700-million-loan-tranche</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 17:26:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行分析显示，奥斯本的紧缩政策导致英国 GDP 损失 2%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/osborne-s-austerity-cost-uk-2-in-lost-gdp-boe-analysis-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据英格兰银行最新发布的研究报告，2010 年保守党上台后乔治·奥斯本 (George Osborne) 的紧缩计划导致英国经济 GDP 损失超过 2%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/osborne-s-austerity-cost-uk-2-in-lost-gdp-boe-analysis-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 17:22:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监管机构称，美国未能充分说明向乌克兰运送武器的情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/us-fails-to-fully-account-for-arms-sent-ukraine-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼的内部监督机构表示，美国未能完全追踪运往乌克兰用于防御俄罗斯的一些最敏感的武器和装备——但没有说任何援助被盗或滥用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/us-fails-to-fully-account-for-arms-sent-ukraine-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 17:15:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管危机加深，布林肯仍称赞中东之行取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/blinken-touts-progress-on-mideast-trip-as-crisis-only-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯表示，美国在中东的合作伙伴已准备好采取措施，以实现该地区的长期稳定——尽管红海的新袭击以及以色列和真主党之间的暴力表明该地区的危机只会变得更加严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/blinken-touts-progress-on-mideast-trip-as-crisis-only-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼监察长将调查奥斯汀住院情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/pentagon-inspector-general-will-probe-austin-hospitalization</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼的内部监督机构宣布，将调查国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀的住院情况，此前他因前列腺手术出现并发症，但几天来没有告诉白宫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/pentagon-inspector-general-will-probe-austin-hospitalization</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:19:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非请求联合国法院命令以色列停止对加沙的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/south-africa-asks-un-court-to-order-israel-to-end-gaza-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非呼吁联合国国际法院命令以色列结束在巴勒斯坦加沙领土上对哈马斯的战争，并裁定其军事行动构成种族灭绝。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/south-africa-asks-un-court-to-order-israel-to-end-gaza-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 12:57:01 GMT</pubDate>
